{"id":"2db2b867-afec-4316-a8ae-4a0dac6eab40","title":"1557/06/16: To Lionardo di Buonarroto Simoni","type":"main-list-block","children":[{"id":"a0413513-80eb-42ad-ae27-eaad58a1755c","type":"standoff-editor-block","text":"From Rome, June 16th, 1557.","standoffProperties":[{"id":"be121c34-f620-4254-b9f8-fc7c483efe74","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":5,"end":8,"value":"501a8a32-2c8a-4934-9060-8c7e36339f0f","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"fb42bd66-6ec4-44db-9979-8a1492f55281","type":"codex/time-reference","start":11,"end":25,"value":"39511ecf-ed2f-4340-a640-6644056baec1","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"10597c96-c92e-4080-86c1-c718bb425a91","type":"style/superscript","start":18,"end":19,"value":null,"zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]}],"blockProperties":[]},{"id":"57e9f7c5-fc85-43e6-bfef-4984ddb58a3b","type":"standoff-editor-block","text":"To Lionardo di Buonarroto Simoni,","standoffProperties":[{"id":"15f15e5d-64d3-4541-a09c-6cf694d8c80f","type":"style/italics","start":0,"end":31,"value":null,"zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"4aa1d53a-ad90-4ca7-af7b-f7db56051295","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":3,"end":31,"value":"93ce2119-f2b8-4642-b551-7b8ca6b1ed96","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]}],"blockProperties":[]},{"id":"f5f872e7-4f31-425c-a6e6-62ab4cd70a4c","type":"standoff-editor-block","text":"in Florence.","standoffProperties":[{"id":"84a87efb-14d8-47e7-ae13-26edb53a6dce","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":3,"end":10,"value":"671ee7e7-ae1b-4a5a-9591-b40203d5108f","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]}],"blockProperties":[]},{"id":"d932bd32-462a-4a4b-b72a-1b5720c54d79","type":"standoff-editor-block","text":"Lionardo,\u00A0\u2014\u00A0I have received the cloth and the silk:\u00A0as soon as I have found somebody to take it I will send it on, and she [Cornelia, Urbino\u0027s widow] will send me the money. Thou wilt let me know about the remainder as soon as thou has done with it as I told thee.","standoffProperties":[{"id":"37ff3fdf-4d55-4804-9914-b5196b273815","type":"style/uppercase","start":0,"end":8,"value":null,"zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"34a7772a-9484-4e7b-a06c-a17f9164dae7","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":0,"end":7,"value":"93ce2119-f2b8-4642-b551-7b8ca6b1ed96","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"3c9c7b92-d098-4a0d-938e-4543a0c32cf7","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":12,"end":12,"value":"add92e01-cefe-4f13-94dd-f00eb82155b0","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"6c03a4a4-4a85-4a25-9e52-5bb6a4c48134","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":63,"end":63,"value":"add92e01-cefe-4f13-94dd-f00eb82155b0","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"b9b215bd-3621-4a3d-aaba-c2efc474b903","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":96,"end":96,"value":"add92e01-cefe-4f13-94dd-f00eb82155b0","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"c4e5ba89-63fc-4ba5-879b-0c796f848410","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":119,"end":121,"value":"6389812f-7018-4969-844d-5b0a03543305","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"0d3dff3d-9bec-4da3-9d3f-740a183c9430","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":124,"end":131,"value":"6389812f-7018-4969-844d-5b0a03543305","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"f2465235-ed31-4665-8ea8-6decfc580bdc","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":134,"end":139,"value":"3a75883e-0f55-44c8-b4d0-3619a6f867ea","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"0424bc63-f5dd-4a8b-9e39-670fbecf15d9","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":143,"end":147,"value":"6389812f-7018-4969-844d-5b0a03543305","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"442b6cf5-0480-4fd8-ac4a-3cf5aaae3f9e","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":160,"end":161,"value":"add92e01-cefe-4f13-94dd-f00eb82155b0","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"eac69962-1845-4a89-bfe3-d4fdcc1a2fee","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":174,"end":177,"value":"93ce2119-f2b8-4642-b551-7b8ca6b1ed96","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"c3c0a334-dcbd-49c8-8909-9c22fee3fa65","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":188,"end":189,"value":"add92e01-cefe-4f13-94dd-f00eb82155b0","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"bd4ca21c-14be-419b-9b7a-03302302670c","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":227,"end":230,"value":"93ce2119-f2b8-4642-b551-7b8ca6b1ed96","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"46ca7ce0-eec4-4444-96d7-9104018026b1","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":252,"end":252,"value":"add92e01-cefe-4f13-94dd-f00eb82155b0","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"86832f3b-1615-4146-95ab-fc09ee9e45fe","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":259,"end":262,"value":"93ce2119-f2b8-4642-b551-7b8ca6b1ed96","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]}],"blockProperties":[]},{"id":"643ff529-6880-498f-a568-a3a8e32c47be","type":"standoff-editor-block","text":"As to my condition, I am in an evil plight, that is to say, I am suffering from all the ailments to which\u00A0old age is subject; the stone, so that I cannot pass water; pains in my side and back, so that oftentimes\u00A0I cannot go up or downstairs. The worst of all is the anxiety which is consuming me, for I have not enough to keep me for three days if I were to let what I have here go to rack and ruin; and although I do not wish on that account to lose the Duke\u0027s favour, neither do I wish to desert the fabric of St. Peter\u0027s, nor to fail in what is due to my own self. Pray God that He will help and counsel me: and if anything should happen to throw me into a\u00A0fever of difficulties I will send immediately for thee. Do not think about it, however, and do not set out without waiting until thou receivest my letter summoning thee.","standoffProperties":[{"id":"b70cc5c9-37f8-450d-8ec5-82adec5230ff","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":6,"end":7,"value":"add92e01-cefe-4f13-94dd-f00eb82155b0","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"679d375d-57ae-4031-bfbf-a906dac31ede","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":20,"end":20,"value":"add92e01-cefe-4f13-94dd-f00eb82155b0","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"5e5e46f7-3527-49a8-982e-8e9f56c88f9f","type":"codex/en